Barcamp Canterbury 3 Artwork
============================

This repo contains artwork for BarCamp Canterbury 3 (2013).

Contents
--------

  * README			- This file
  * bc-cant3.xcf		- GIMP project
  * bc-cant3.png		- Hi-res flattened PNG.
  * bc-cant3-webres.png		- Web-res flattened PNG (1700 wide).
  * bc-cant3-webres-small	- Smaller web-res flattened PNG (800 wide).
  * bc-cant3-logo-only.png	- Hi-res logo only (no text).
  * bc-cant3-dated-webres-small.png
			- Smaller web-res flattened PNG with date (800 wide).
  * bc-cant3-dated-webres.png	- Web-res flattened PNG with date (1700 wide).
  * bc-cant3-dated.png		- Hi-res flattened PNG with date.

Fonts
-----

  * Century Gothic
  * Century Gothic Bold

